---
title: Indonesian Turkey Rendang with Basmati Rice
description: Rendang is one of the national dishes of Indonesia! Its tender, caramelized turkey seasoned with lemon grass and spices is the star of the show! Served over fluffy basmati rice to capture all that tasty sauce!
